https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dGefoUIQg8vN4AVMTePp09To1pR.jpg It's the Activist vs. the Analyst in a witty spoof of issue oriented talk shows like Larry King and The O'Reilly Factor. Host Jerome X, a black activist, interviews the late great Sigmund Freud who is reincarnated in his doll form, complete with a cigar and a willingness to blame it all on Mom. The voice of reason is plastic. Dolls with Issues
